      "text": "it's cool.  The origin of \"Mr\" is actually not gendered per se.\n\nIt comes from an indication of professional quality of craft, back in the old medieval guild days.  Mr -eq \"Master\", as in Master crasftperson.\n\nGranted, guilds were exclusionary, but mostly on a professional quality level."
